### Architectural Concerns (added to tech-debt.md)
1. **GameCanvas duplicate sprite loading** — `loadSprites` callback and `useEffect` both implement identical sprite-loading logic; `fps` change triggers full reload unnecessarily. (Medium)
2. **ComparisonView ZoomPanel doesn't reuse ZoomContainer** — ZoomPanel reimplements zoom/display logic that ZoomContainer already handles better (pan, max zoom, hover grid). Should consolidate. (Medium)
